OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FA West Yorkshire Police trainee who
OL,7,Ftook his own life told his university
OL,8,Ftutor that his sergeant was 'harsh'
OL,9,Fbut not a racist bully, an inquest
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FAnugrah Abraham, 21, from Bury,
OL,13,FGreater Manchester, feared he was not
OL,14,Fcut out to be a police officer and was
OL,15,Fstruggling with stress and anxiety,
OL,16,Fthe hearing at Rochdale Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt was told.
OL,19,FHe had also suffered nightmares about
OL,20,Fhis station sergeant, which left him
OL,21,Ffeeling afraid he could be dismissed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
