OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FMr Abraham, who was training at
OL,7,FHalifax police station, reportedly
OL,8,Fexperienced bullying and racism
OL,9,Fallegations which West Yorkshire
OL,10,FPolice (WYP) have denied.
OL,12,FHis father had previously claimed his
OL,13,Fson faced racism while working as a
OL,14,Ftrainee.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard that Mr Abraham,
OL,17,Fdescribed as "intelligent, polite and
OL,18,Flovely" by his university progress
OL,19,Ftutor, felt he had led a "sheltered"
OL,20,Flife and was shocked by the culture of
OL,21,Fpolice work.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
