OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FHe had also been juggling the
OL,7,Fpressures of a full-time role as a
OL,8,Fpolice officer with a degree
OL,9,Fapprenticeship at Leeds Trinity
OL,10,FUniversity.
OL,12,FWhile there were no concerns about his
OL,13,Facademic work, Mr Abraham had been
OL,14,Fplaced on a development programme due
OL,15,Fto difficulties with his practical
OL,16,Fpolice training.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
