OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FLyn Farrell, his progress tutor, told
OL,7,Fthe inquest that during a meeting on
OL,8,F19 January 2023, two months before Mr
OL,9,FAbraham's death, he told her he no
OL,10,Flonger wanted to be a police officer.
OL,12,FMs Farrell said he felt ill-prepared
OL,13,Ffor the challenges of the job and had
OL,14,Fbeen shocked by certain aspects of
OL,15,Fpolice work, including being
OL,16,Fcriticised for being the "last person
OL,17,Fout of the car" during incidents.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
