OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FMr Abraham's tutor also revealed that
OL,7,Fshe was unaware he had been referred
OL,8,Fto occupational health following
OL,9,Fthoughts of self-harm and suicide.
OL,11,FShe expressed surprise that this
OL,12,Finformation had not been communicated
OL,13,Fto her. "He was exactly the sort of
OL,14,Fofficer they advertised they wanted,"
OL,15,FMs Farrell said.
OL,17,F"He was articulate, intelligent,
OL,18,Fpolite and lovely. My only fear was
OL,19,Fthat he might drop out of the course,
OL,20,Fbut I didn't know about the other
OL,21,Fstruggles he was facing."
