OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FMr Abraham was found dead on 4 March
OL,7,F2023, the same day he was due back to
OL,8,Fwork after a two-week break.
OL,10,FThe inquest also heard that Mr Abraham
OL,11,Fwas asked whether his sargeant was
OL,12,Fbullying or being racist towards him.
OL,13,FHe responded that while his sergeant's
OL,14,Ftraining style was "harsh", it was not
OL,15,Ftargeted at him personally, and he did
OL,16,Fnot believe his sergeant was being
OL,17,Fracist or a bully.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
