OL,3,CPolice trainee told tutor sergeant was
OL,4,C'harsh' but not a racist bully
OL,6,FThe inquest raised concerns about a
OL,7,Fwider problem in policing, with the
OL,8,Fissue being raised of many police
OL,9,Fofficers coming into the profession
OL,10,Fyounger and being managed by less
OL,11,Fexperienced colleagues.
OL,13,FThere has been a significant increase
OL,14,Fin officers requesting welfare
OL,15,Fsupport, as well as higher dropout
OL,16,Frates among degree apprenticeship
OL,17,Frecruits.
OL,19,FThe force has since reduced the number
OL,20,Fof recruits coming through the degree
OL,21,Fapprenticeship pathway.
